    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, trim and thinly slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> (Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 pans!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1720168810813-x200.jpg",
