            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the steaks are cooking, add your<strong> sweetcorn cobette[s] </strong>to a<strong> </strong>heatproof bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Cover the bowl with <strong>cling film </strong>and pierce a few holes in the top</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until the corn is tender</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1720168818461-x200.jpg",
