            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, add the <strong>drained black beans</strong> to the <strong>seasoned rice</strong></p><p>Stir together and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving – this is your <strong>black bean rice</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the<strong> remaining roasted garlic paste</strong> to the reserved pan, off the heat</p><p>Tip: Be careful, the garlic paste will sizzle from the heat of the oil!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1720168823823-x200.jpg",
