            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[70ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [90ml] </span><strong>cold water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and any <strong>resting juices</strong> from the steak[s]</p><p>Stir it all together, return the pan to a medium heat and bring to the boil</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook for 1 min or until thickened – this is your <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>chipotle sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
