          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1720168829643-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>rested steak[s] </strong>finely on a clean board</p><p>Serve the<strong> sliced steak</strong> over the <strong>black bean rice</strong> with the <strong>corn cobette[s]</strong> to the side</p><p>Top the <strong>corn cobette[s]</strong> with a small knob of<strong> butter</strong></p><p>Drizzle the<strong> spicy chipotle sauce</strong> over the steak and garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
